&lt;p&gt;Thank you for reading (viewing the pictures).&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Note: This article was first published in my retired &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.reasonwhyy.blogspot.com&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;blog&lt;/a&gt; on 16 February 2020. This is a copy of it.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Arunachal is one of the most beautiful states in India, and surely more people need to go and appreciate it&amp;rsquo;s beauty when they can in this pandemic.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
